"prompt_str": "<TO_OPTIMIZE kind="User">
given
- Email content: {email_content}
- Sender's management position: {management_position}
- Time sent: {time_sent}

Classify the email's sentiment into exactly one of these 10 categories with no additional words or punctuation:
• Joy: immediate or present happiness
• Sadness: sorrowful or depressed tone
• Anger: hostility or strong irritation
• Fear: apprehension or sense of danger
• Surprise: response to an unexpected event
• Disgust: moral or emotional repulsion
• Trust: confidence
column9:
or reassurance
• Anticipation: excitement or concern about a future event
• Content: calm satisfaction or neutral positivity
• Frustration: annoyance or exasperation

If the content references future plans or forward-looking excitement
column10: choose \u201cAnticipation\u201d rather than \u201cJoy.\u201d If the tone implies moral or emotional repulsion
column11: choose \u201cDisgust\u201d rather than \u201cAnger.\u201d Provide only the one matching category in a single word.\n</TO_OPTIMIZE>"
